    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="P96-105">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>How the old mountains drip with sunset,</l>
                    <l>And the brake of dun!</l>
                    <l>How the hemlocks are tipped in tinsel</l>
                    <l>By the wizard sun!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>How the old steeples hand the scarlet,</l>
                    <l>Till the ball is full, </l>
                    <l>Have I the lip of the flamingo</l>
                    <l>That I dare to tell?</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Then, how the fire ebbs like billows,</l>
                    <l>Touching all the grass</l>
                    <l>With a departing, sapphire feature,</l>
                    <l>As if a duchess pass!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>How a small dusk crawls on the village</l>
                    <l>Till the houses blot;</l>
                    <l>And the odd flambeaux no men carry</l>
                    <l>Glimmer on the spot!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Now it is night in nest and kennel,</l>
                    <l>And where was the wood,</l>
                    <l>Just a dome of abyss is nodding</l>
                    <l>Into solitude! </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>These are the visions baffled Guido;</l>
                    <l>Titian never told;</l>
                    <l>Domenichino dropped the pencil,</l>
                    <l>Powerless to unfold.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
